[84.980499, "o", "\u001b[1;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m                                                                                       \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[2;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m These tools live in this project's \u001b[36m.brainyard/tools/\u001b[0m and are callable as \u001b[36muser$<name>\u001b[0m: \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[3;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m                                                                                       \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[4;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mTool\u001b[0m            \u001b[2m в”Ӯ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mDescription\u001b[0m                            \u001b[2m в”Ӯ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mInput\u001b[0m                    \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[5;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m \u001b[2mв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\u001b[0m           \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[6;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m \u001b[36muser$count-lines\u001b[0m\u001b[2m в”Ӯ \u001b[0mCount newline-separated lines in a file\u001b[2m в”Ӯ \u001b[0m\u001b[36m:path\u001b[0m (string)           \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[7;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m \u001b[36muse"]
[84.980618, "o", "r$shout-test\u001b[0m \u001b[2m в”Ӯ \u001b[0mUppercase the text                     \u001b[2m в”Ӯ \u001b[0m\u001b[36m:text\u001b[0m (string)           \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[8;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m                                                                                       \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[9;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m   вҖў \u001b[1;97m2 tools\u001b[0m registered.                                                               \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[10;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m   вҖў Want to inspect a body (\u001b[36mtools$read\u001b[0m), refine, or author a new one? Just say so.    \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[11;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\u001b[0m\u001b[12;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[13;1H\u001b[2K                                                                  \u001b[2m2 calls в”Ӯ 56,498 tokens в”Ӯ $0.2352\u001b[0m\u001b[14;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[1m\u001b[96m\u001b[100mвқҜ Create a new persistent tool named count-words "]
[84.980907, "o", "that takes a file path and returns the number of\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K  whitespace-separated words in that file's content.\u001b[0m\u001b[17;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92mвң“\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 1 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(60446 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(55.6s)\u001b[0m\u001b[18;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mTask: author a persistent tool `count-words`. Prior turn established only \u001b[0m\u001b[19;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2m`user$count-lines` and `user$shout-test` exist, so no collision. I'll compose `read-file` \u001b[0m\u001b[20;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mand count non-whitespace runs via `re-seq #\"\\S+\"` (handles empty files вҶ’ 0). Dry-run with \u001b[0m\u001b[21;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mtools$validate first, sampling against an existing file (~/.brainyard/BRAINYARD.md) to \u001b[0m\u001b[22;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mconfirm behavior before tools$create.\u001b[0m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[2K  \u001b[36mвҶ’\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mtools$validate\u001b[0m({\"name\" \"count-words\", \"body\" \"(fn [args] (let [path (:pa...): called \u001b[2mвҶ’\u001b[0m \u001b[92mdone\u001b[0m, 9ms, 90 chars\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;96m+\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 2 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(4.4s)\u001b[0m\u001b[25;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b"]
[84.981116, "o", "[0m\u001b[2mThe dry-run validated cleanly (`:valid true`, `:collision false`, body+schema OK). Now \u001b[0m\u001b[26;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mI'll persist the tool with `tools$create`.\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;93mв ј\u001b[0m\u001b[2m]\u001b[0m \u001b[96mRuminating...\u001b[0m\u001b[2m (59.9s)\u001b[0m\u001b[28;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2mв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\u001b[0m"]
