[112.925163, "o", "\u001b[1;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mName\u001b[0m       \u001b[2m в”Ӯ \u001b[0m\u001b[36mcount-words\u001b[0m                                                                  \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[2;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mDescription\u001b[0m\u001b[2m в”Ӯ \u001b[0mCount whitespace-separated words in a file's content given its path          \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[3;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mInput\u001b[0m      \u001b[2m в”Ӯ \u001b[0m\u001b[36m:path\u001b[0m (string) вҖ” file path to count words for                                \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[4;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mReturns\u001b[0m    \u001b[2m в”Ӯ \u001b[0m\u001b[36m{:words N}\u001b[0m on success, \u001b[36m{:error \"...\"}\u001b[0m if the file can't be read              \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[5;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m                                                                                            \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[6;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mBody\u001b[0m (composes \u001b[36mread-file\u001b[0m, counts non-whitespace runs):                                     \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[7;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m(fn [args]\u001b[0m                                                                                "]
[112.925211, "o", " \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[8;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m  (let [path    (:path args)\u001b[0m                                                               \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[9;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m        content (:content (read-file {:path path}))]\u001b[0m                                       \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[10;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m    (if content\u001b[0m                                                                            \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[11;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m      {:words (count (re-seq #\"\\S+\" content))}\u001b[0m                                             \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[12;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36m      {:error (str \"Could not read file: \" path)})))\u001b[0m                                       \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[13;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m                                                                                            \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[14;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m   вҖў \u001b[1;97mVerified:\u001b[0m \u001b[36muser$count-words {:path \"~/.brainyard/BRAINYARD.md\"}\u001b[0m вҶ’ \u001b[36m{:words 13}\u001b[0m вң“         \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m "]
[112.925346, "o", "  вҖў Empty/whitespace-only files correctly return \u001b[36m{:words 0}\u001b[0m.                               \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m                                                                                            \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[17;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m Want to inspect, refine, or author another? Just say so.                                   \u001b[92mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\u001b[18;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92mв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\u001b[0m\u001b[19;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[20;1H\u001b[2K                                                                 \u001b[2m5 calls в”Ӯ 149,443 tokens в”Ӯ $0.4701\u001b[0m\u001b[21;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[22;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[1m\u001b[96m\u001b[100mвқҜ Read back the count-words tool you just created, then run it on docs/tutorials/README.md and\u001b[23;1H\u001b[2K  report the word count.\u001b[0m\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;96m+\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97m"]
